  "instructions": [
    "In a large copper pot, heat the sesame oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the sliced pork belly and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional minute.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the gochujang, soy sauce, and brown sugar.",
    "Pour the sauce into the copper pot and stir to combine.",
    "Add the diced kiwifruit and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Garnish with chopped green onions and toasted sesame seeds.",
    "Serve the deopbap hot, straight from the copper pot.",
    "Knead the dough to make a soft and fluffy texture, if desired.",
    "Let it rest for a few minutes before serving."
